				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ok, slow isn't REQUIRED for Tier one...if you have a lvl 65 tank and a damn good cleric. 
<br />

<br />
In case you missed it, we arn't asking to nerf BL's, I think they do OK. I'm (other may be) not asking for slow in ANY form, nor root or snare. I am asking for an upgrade to a spell we have had since lvl 4?? (Maybe 9). I still don't think that will allow us to solo tier 2-3 stuff very well, but I can grab flies/etc in PoD for some XP while I am LFG or have little time. You should review what you post, as I have NEVER asked to nerf BL heals, only enhance mage ones to the level of Bst heals. We are pet masters, we should be able to heal like them.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=542302" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://myweb.cableone.net/nweaver/gryyf.jpg" border="0" /></a>
